UPDATE cities SET connection_description = 'My current city, where my AWS and tech journey continue to grow. You can usually find me at The Lab downtown in the Palm Tower Suites working on my tech game. Don''t sleep on Sarasota. This is the home of the Sarasota.Tech community, launched with no marketing budget and fueled entirely by word of mouth, it has exploded from a handful of friends to more than 3,000 builders, founders, and cloud professionals in just two years. Sarasota isn''t just a beach town anymore, it''s becoming a launchpad for modern, cloud-native innovation.' WHERE id = 'sarasota';

UPDATE cities SET connection_description = 'My former home for more than 11 years, where I served as a coach, recruiter, and educator at Albright College. As Associate Head Coach and Offensive Coordinator, I was part of seven championship teams, five NCAA Division III playoff appearances, and coached over 50 all-conference players. This is where my foundations in education, coaching, character, leadership, and communication were built. Albright also has a strong link to the tech world, one of YouTube''s early co-founding members, behind one of the most influential SaaS platforms in history, is an Albright College graduate.' WHERE id = 'reading';